      <title>重要的巴尔的摩大桥被船撞后倒塌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/vehicles-plunge-into-water-after-ship-rams-into-baltimore-bridge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴尔的摩的一座主要通勤桥梁在被一艘集装箱船撞击后倒塌，导致车辆落入水中，并导致美国东海岸最重要港口之一的航运交通中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/vehicles-plunge-into-water-after-ship-rams-into-baltimore-bridge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:57:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
